BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 123.84 600 Td (How AI Can Help You Plan) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 80 585 m 352 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 555 Td (Welcome to a new way of planning your day! AI tools like ChatGPT,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 537 Td (Siri, and Google Assistant can help you organize your life effortlessly.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 509 Td (Each daily page in this planner includes an 'Ask AI' suggestion -) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 491 Td (a prompt you can try with ChatGPT or your voice assistant.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 463 Td (How to use this planner:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 445 Td (1. Start each morning by reading the AI suggestion for the day.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 427 Td (2. Try the prompt with ChatGPT or your preferred AI tool.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 409 Td (3. Write down your priorities and schedule for the day.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 391 Td (4. In the evening, note what AI tool you tried and what you learned.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 373 Td (5. Track your wellness: sleep, water intake, and steps.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 345 Td (You do not need to use AI every day - go at your own pace.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 327 Td (Even trying one new AI prompt per week will build your confidence.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 299 Td (Remember: AI is your assistant, not your boss. You are in control!) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
